{"data":[{"name":"83:1","price":"伤哉！称量不公的人们。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُطَفِّفِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5849,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:2","price":"当他们从别人称量进来的时候，他们称量得很充足；","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ إِذَا ٱكۡتَالُواْ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ يَسۡتَوۡفُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5850,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:3","price":"当他们量给别人或称给别人的时候，他们不称足不量足。","arabic":"وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمۡ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمۡ يُخۡسِرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5851,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:4","price":"难道他们不信自己将复活，","arabic":"أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5852,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:5","price":"在一个重大的日子吗？","arabic":"لِيَوۡمٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5853,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:6","price":"在那日，人们将为全世界的主而起立。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلنَّاسُ لِرَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5854,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:7","price":"绝不然，恶人们的册薄确在森吉尼之中。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5855,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:8","price":"你怎能知道森吉尼是什么？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سِجِّينٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5856,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:9","price":"是一本封存的薄子。","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5857,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:10","price":"在那日，伤哉否认的人们。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5858,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:11","price":"否认报应日的人们！","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يُكَذِّبُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5859,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:12","price":"只有每个过分的犯罪的人，否认它。","arabic":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهِۦٓ إِلَّا كُلُّ مُعۡتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5860,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:13","price":"当别人对他宣读我的天经的时候，他说：“这是古人的故事。”","arabic":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5861,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:14","price":"绝不然，但他们所犯的罪恶，已像锈一样蒙蔽他们的心。","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَلۡۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5862,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:15","price":"真的，在那日，他们必受阻拦，不得觐见他们的主。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّمَحۡجُوبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5863,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:16","price":"然后，他们必堕入烈火之中。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5864,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:17","price":"然后，或者将对他们说：“这就是你们所否认的。”","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُقَالُ هَٰذَا ٱلَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5865,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:18","price":"真的，善人们的册薄在恩林伊中。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارِ لَفِي عِلِّيِّينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5866,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:19","price":"你怎能知道恩林伊是什么？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا عِلِّيُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5867,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:20","price":"是一本封存的薄子，","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5868,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:21","price":"安拉所亲近的天使们将作证它。","arabic":"يَشۡهَدُهُ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5869,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:22","price":"善人们必在恩泽中，","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5870,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:23","price":"靠在床上注视着，","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5871,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:24","price":"你能在他们的面目上认识恩泽的光华。","arabic":"تَعۡرِفُ فِي وُجُوهِهِمۡ نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5872,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:25","price":"他们将饮封存的天醇，","arabic":"يُسۡقَوۡنَ مِن رَّحِيقٖ مَّخۡتُومٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5873,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:26","price":"封瓶口的，是麝香。教贪爱这种幸福的人们，争先为善吧！","arabic":"خِتَٰمُهُۥ مِسۡكٞۚ وَفِي ذَٰلِكَ فَلۡيَتَنَافَسِ ٱلۡمُتَنَٰفِسُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5874,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:27","price":"天醇的混合物，是由太斯尼姆来的，","arabic":"وَمِزَاجُهُۥ مِن تَسۡنِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5875,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:28","price":"那是一洞泉水，安拉所亲近的人将饮它。","arabic":"عَيۡنٗا يَشۡرَبُ بِهَا ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5876,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:29","price":"犯罪的人们常常嘲笑信士们，","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ أَجۡرَمُواْ كَانُواْ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5877,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:30","price":"当信士们从他们的面前走过的时候，他们以目互相示意；","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَرُّواْ بِهِمۡ يَتَغَامَزُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5878,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:31","price":"当他们回家的时候，洋洋得意地回去；","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱنقَلَبُوٓاْ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِمُ ٱنقَلَبُواْ فَكِهِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5879,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:32","price":"当他们遇见信士们的时候，他们说：“这等人确是迷误的。”","arabic":"وَإِذَا رَأَوۡهُمۡ قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ لَضَآلُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5880,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:33","price":"他们没有被派去监视信士们。","arabic":"وَمَآ أُرۡسِلُواْ عَلَيۡهِمۡ حَٰفِظِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5881,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:34","price":"故今日信士们，嘲笑不信道的人们，","arabic":"فَٱلۡيَوۡمَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ مِنَ ٱلۡكُفَّارِ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5882,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:35","price":"他们靠在床上注视着，","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5883,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"83:36","price":"不信道的人们已获得他们的行为的报酬了吗？","arabic":"هَلۡ ثُوِّبَ ٱلۡكُفَّارُ مَا كَانُواْ يَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5884,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin","Chapter Al-Mutaffifin","Mutaffifin","Surah Mutaffifin","Chapter Mutaffifin","Al Mutaffifin","Surah Al Mutaffifin","Chapter Al Mutaffifin","Surah 83","Chapter 83","Defrauding","المطففين"]}